<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_60_r1l5"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> vvılhelm als dır auch wol <expan>wıſſenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ıſt . daʒ es <expan>ıecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> ſörglıch in </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l6">den <expan>lande<ex>n</ex></expan> ſteet / <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> vns ʒu mal <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd niht lıeb ıſt / daʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l7"><expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd kawffleẅt hab vnd gut ſo <expan>ſam<ex>m</ex>enthaft</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>auf</expan> mıt ein = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l9"><expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> gee . als vor her <expan>gewönl<ex>ich</ex></expan> beſchehen 
<add><ab facs="#facs_60_line_1573123739860_976">ıſt </ab></add> . vnd ıſt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_60_r1l8">auch </ab></add> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>mainu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> . daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l10">der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hab vnd gut in vıer teıl geordinıert vnd geteılt wurd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l11"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>auf</expan> ʒe geen . Als wır das ſebolt Pfıncʒıng befolhen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . mıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l12">dein vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> kawffleẅt rat daniden alſo <expan>ʒubeſtell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l13">wan der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> ſebolt Pfıncʒıng ʒu <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıgſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l14"><expan>Römiſch<ex>en</ex></expan> künıg . <expan>vollreıte<ex>n</ex></expan> wırt / <expan>beſorg<ex>en</ex></expan> wır daʒ dıe <expan>ordnu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l15">niht <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> möcht <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . Vnd <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır dıch vnd <expan>befelh<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l17">dır daʒ du 
<add><ab facs="#facs_60_r1l16">dıch </ab></add> der ſache annemeſt vnd dıe mıt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> kawffleẅt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l19">rat 
<add><ab facs="#facs_60_r1l18">von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab></add> . alſo beſtelleſt vnd ordiniereſt / daʒ auch das <expan>gehalt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l20">denn <expan>welh<ex>er</ex></expan> der <expan>vnſ<ex>ern</ex></expan> des niht gehorſam wölt ſein . den mainen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l21">wır <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒe <expan>ſtraff<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd laſſeſt dır dıe ſache <expan>empfolh<ex>en</ex></expan> ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l23">als wır dir getrawn vnd als des 
<add><ab facs="#facs_60_r1l22">ein </ab></add> notdurft ıſt . Daran tuſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l26">du <expan>gencʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_60_line_1573124254494_1006">vvıllen </ab></add> . vnd <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch dıe mü <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gen dır <expan>erkenn<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l27">Vnd auf das <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> wır dır hie mıt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> an den <expan>gemeine<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l28"><expan>kawffma<ex>n</ex></expan> / den laſſ ſıe <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> . daʒ ſıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>meinu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vnd ernſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l29">darinne ſehen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l30"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>vıgı<ex>lia</ex></expan> Egıdij / <note place="inline"> vnd derſelb brief </note> </ab>
<note place="inline"><ab facs="#facs_60_r1l31">iſt cʒu <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>ſt</expan> an diſem buch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒeıhe<ex>n</ex>t</expan> / als man <expan>den<ex>n</ex></expan> den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_60_r1l32"><expan>gemaine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>kaufleut<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>gepot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat / </ab>
</note>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_60" id="30r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Wilhelm<ex>en</ex></expan> Mendel, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und <expan>ratg<ex>esellen</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Wilhelm, als dir auch wol
                                <expan>wissenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ist, daz es
                                <expan>jecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> sörglich in den
                                <expan>lande<ex>n</ex></expan> steet, <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
                        uns zu mal <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> und niht lieb ist, daz
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und kawfflewt hab und gut so
                                <expan>sam<ex>m</ex>enthaft</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>auf</expan> mit ein<expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> gee, als
                        vor her <expan>gewönl<ex>ich</ex></expan> beschehen <add>ist</add>, und ist
                            <add>auch</add>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>mainu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>, daz der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hab
                        und gut in vier teil geordiniert und geteilt wurd
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>auf</expan> ze geen, als wir das Sebolt Pfinczing
                        befolhen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, mit dein und
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> kawfflewt rat daniden also <expan>zu
                                bestell<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und wan der
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Sebolt Pfinczing zu
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigst<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan> dem <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan> künig,
                                <expan>vollreite<ex>n</ex></expan> wirt,
                            <expan>besorg<ex>en</ex></expan> wir, daz die
                            <expan>ordnu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> also niht
                            <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> möcht <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>.
                        Und <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir dich und <expan>befelh<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        dir, daz du <add>dich</add> der sache annemest und die mit
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> kawfflewt rat <add>von
                                    <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan></add> also bestellest und ordinierest, daz
                        auch das <expan>gehalt<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>; denn <expan>welh<ex>er</ex></expan> der
                                <expan>uns<ex>ern</ex></expan> des niht gehorsam wölt sein, den
                        mainen wir <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ze
                            <expan>straff<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und lassest dir die sache
                                <expan>empfolh<ex>en</ex></expan> sein, als wir dir getrawn und als
                        des <add>ein</add> notdurft ist, daran tust du
                            <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<add>willen</add>. Und <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch die mü
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gen dir
                            <expan>erkenn<ex>en</ex></expan> und auf das
                            <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> wir dir hie mit
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> an den <expan>gemeine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>kawffma<ex>n</ex></expan>; den lass sie
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan>, daz sie
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>meinu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und ernst darinne
                        sehen. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan> Egidii.
<app>
<note place="inline">Und derselb brief ist czu <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>st</expan> an disem
                                buch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>czeihe<ex>n</ex>t,</expan> als man
                                        <expan>den<ex>n</ex></expan> den
                                    <expan>gemaine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>kaufleut<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                    <expan>gepot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat. </note>
</app></ab>
</div>
</div></body>
